    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - Safexpress - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Join the Safexpress family as a Supply Chain Manager in Ranchi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Safexpress:\nSafexpress is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Safexpress!",
